game.name: Fashion Dress Design Studio
game.description:
Many girls want to run their fashion studio. But, only a few get a chance to make it come true due to their hard work, dedication and financial support. Luckily, we have got you covered with a wonderful brand new dressing game where you are playing the role of a fashion designer. Would you like to try your hands in this new kind of puzzle? Join Fashion Dress Design Studio game and get ready to design a fabulous outfit in your own fashion studio!
You will find all things in a studio that you need to complete your task. Start your girls game with preparing a perfect outfit and then coming up to give her a complete makeover! Choose from plenty of dress options, suitable earrings, stylish hairstyles, a pair of trendy shoes and a sparkling necklace! Everything will be in your hands right from selecting the right kind of style and fabric to the matching colors in this online princess design game. 
Make sure to stitch every portion of the dress using the virtual sewing machine. You will get here a fabulous opportunity to show the world that you have unique style sense. Grab this chance and try to complete all the steps to create a new style dress for your virtual girl in this html5 princess dress up game! Click the Reset button in case if you want to start it again from the middle or the end! Enjoy a lot in our all online girls games where you can keep you busy without download!
